title: Guns found at Sean 'Diddy' Combs’ L.A. and Miami properties during federal searches, sources say
description: Federal agents found firearms during searches of properties belonging to Sean "Diddy" Combs in both Los Angeles and Miami, according to three sources familiar with the matter told NBC News on Tuesday.

title: NBC News cuts ties with former RNC Chair Ronna McDaniel
description: NBC News has reversed its decision to hire former Republican National Committee chairwoman Ronna McDaniel as a political analyst after network executives faced a chorus of fierce on-air criticism.

title: Unfounded conspiracy theories spread online after Baltimore bridge collapse
description: Outlandish conspiracy theories circulated on X after a container ship collided with a major bridge in Maryland, causing it to collapse, early Tuesday morning.

title: Some creators say they’re frustrated after Instagram starts limiting political content recommendations
description: Instagram creators who frequently post about news and politics are urging their followers to allow “political content” in their feeds after the platform began automatically limiting such posts.

title: Biden says he wants federal government to pay for rebuilding of Baltimore bridge after cargo ship crash
description: WASHINGTON — President Joe Biden said he wants the federal government to pay for the reconstruction of the Baltimore bridge that collapsed early Tuesday morning after a large cargo ship sailed straight into one of the bridge's support pillars.

title: Massive engineering task lies ahead after the Baltimore bridge collapse
description: The Frances Scott Key Bridge collapse has brought one of the nation's busiest ports to a standstill. NBC News' Tom Costello says clearing the debris and reopening the port is an immediate area of focus.

title: Eva Mendes talks career, motherhood — and sponge business!
description: Actor Eva Mendes sits down with Shop TODAY editorial director Adrianna Brach to talk about growing up in a "very Cuban household," being a mother of two and her relationship with Ryan Gosling. Plus, get some exclusive deals on products from Skura Style, a sponge business she now co-owns with the founders.

title: Key Bridge collapse is 'absolute tragedy,' Baltimore official says
description: Baltimore County Executive John A. Olszewski Jr. joins TODAY and says the "primary efforts are around search and rescue" after the Francis Scott Key Bridge collapsed when it was hit by a cargo ship. "It's an absolute tragedy," he says.

title: Rescue operation underway after Baltimore's Key Bridge collapses
description: A cargo container ship crashed into Baltimore’s Francis Scott Key Bridge early Tuesday morning, sending the structure collapsing into the harbor. Cars and people plunged into the river, setting off a frantic rescue operation. NBC’s Tom Costello reports for TODAY.

title: Supreme Court weighs challenge to abortion pill's widespread availability
description: The Supreme Court hears arguments on whether to maintain access to abortion pill mifepristone as it weighs a high-stakes challenge to the FDA's drug approval process.

title: Video shows Maryland bridge collapsing after ship collision
description: A major bridge in Baltimore, Maryland, partially collapsed after a ship collided into the Francis Scott Key Bridge, possibly leaving a number of people in the river below, authorities said.

title: Major bridge in Maryland collapses after being hit by a ship
description: The Francis Scott Key bridge in Baltimore, Maryland, partially collapsed early Tuesday, police said. It was hit by a ship, officials said.
